{
  "title": "Cooling Crunchy Syrian Beetroot Salad",
  "description": "A salty and springy Syrian dish featuring cooked beetroot, perfect for a quick fix, with anti-inflammatory friendly ingredients. This salad is great for a light lunch or snack.",
